    dc:description "FIGURES 26 – 30. Heteroisotoma heteronomica sp. nov.: 26, macrosetae, sensillae and p-row of setae on body tergites (area of location of pseudosensilla marked with dotted line); 27, 28, dorsal chaetotaxy of Abd. I (27) and II (28); 29, macrosetae of body tergites; 30, chaetotaxy of dorsal side of Abd. IV – VI; s, accp, as: macrosensillum, ms: microsensillum, s': pseudosensillum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/203954/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.203951>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6, 7. Heteroisotoma sinorossica sp. nov.: 6, chaetotaxy of dorsal side of Abd. IV-VI; 7, macrosetae, sensillae and prow of common setae on body tergites; s, accp, as: macrosensillum, ms: microsensillum, s': \" pseudosensillum \", Mac-s: filament-like macroseta." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/203951/files/figure.png" ;
